## Third-Party Components

This project includes or uses the following third-party components:

### Vive_Tracker
- Source: https://github.com/snuvclab/Vive_Tracker
- License: See Vive_Tracker/LICENSE
- Used for: HTC Vive Tracker 3.0 interface

### xArm Python SDK
- Source: https://github.com/xArm-Developer/xArm-Python-SDK
- License: BSD-3-Clause
- Used for: xArm robot control

### inspire_hands
- Source: https://github.com/Sentdex/inspire_hands
- License: MIT
- Used for: Inspire Hand gripper control (RH56 series)

### Meta Quest Hand Tracking
- Uses Meta's XR SDK for Unity
- Subject to Meta's SDK license terms
